<!doctype html><html lang="en"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"><title>go-htmx — notes</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/app.css"><script src="/static/js/htmx.min.js"></script><script src="/static/js/hx-sse.min.js"></script></head><body><h1>Notes</h1><p>Example feature: a live, multi-client notes list over Server-Sent Events (Story #4, AD-4's real-time layer).</p><form hx-post="/notes" hx-swap="none" hx-on::after:request="this.reset()"><input type="text" name="body" placeholder="Write a note…" autocomplete="off" required> <button type="submit">Add</button></form><p><span id="notes-count" hx-swap-oob="true">2 notes</span></p><div id="notes-stream" hx-sse:connect="/notes/stream" hx-target="#notes-list" hx-swap="afterbegin" style="display:none"></div><div id="notes-list"><div class="note" id="note-2"><p>second note</p><time>2026-01-15 10:35:00</time></div><div class="note" id="note-1"><p>first note</p><time>2026-01-15 10:30:00</time></div></div></body></html>